embeds.title: ▬▬▬ :notebook_with_decorative_cover: __**Server Information**__ :notebook_with_decorative_cover: ▬▬▬
embeds.description:
⠀
```This discord server is a hub for professionals, students, and hobbyists interested in learning, sharing, and collaborating. We want to keep it that way. This server promotes learning and the sharing of learning resources in all fields of Infosec and cybersecurity. Here, you will find like-minded individuals who are interested in furthering their knowledge and contributing back to the community. You can and will learn a lot from experienced users on the server, however, this server is not a tech support hub where you ask questions whose answers can easily be found with a 3 second Google search.```
